\c 21
\s Vana vaIsraeri vanorwiswa neVaKenani
\p
\v 1 Zvino mambo weAradhi muKenani waiva agere kunyika yekuchamhembe\x + 33.40. Vato. 1.16.\x* wakanzwa kuti Israeri wouya nenzira yevashori, ipapo akarwisa Israeri, ndokutapa nhapwa kubva kwavari\x + 13.21.\x*.
\v 2 Israeri ndokupika mhiko kuna Jehovha, ndokuti\x + Gen. 28.20. Vato. 11.30.\x*: Kana mukapa kwazvo vanhu ava muruoko rwangu, ipapo ndichaparadza kwazvo maguta avo\x + Rev. 27.28,29.\x*.
\v 3 Jehovha ndokuteerera kuinzwi raIsraeri, ndokupa VaKenani \add kwavari\add*; zvino vakavaparadza chose nemaguta avo; naizvozvo wakatumidza nzvimbo iyo Horima.
\p
\v 4 Zvino vakabva pagomo reHori nenzira yeGungwa Dzvuku\x + 20.22; 33.41.\x* kuti vanyenyeredze nyika yaEdhomu; mweya wevanhu ndokuodzwa nekuda kwenzira\x + Vato. 11.18.\x*.
\v 5 Vanhu ndokutaura vachipikisana naMwari uye vachipikisana naMozisi\x + Map. 78.19.\x*, \add vakati\add*: Makatikwidzirei kutibudisa muEgipita kuzofira murenje? Nokuti hapana zvekudya uye hapana mvura\x + Eki. 16.3; 17.3.\x*; zvino mweya wedu unosema zvekudya izvi zvisingabatsiri\x + 11.6.\x*.
\v 6 Zvino Jehovha wakatuma nyoka dzinopisa pakati pevanhu\x + Det. 8.15; 1 VaKori. 10.9. Isa. 14.29; 30.6.\x* ndokuruma vanhu; vanhu vazhinji vaIsraeri ndokufa\x + Jer. 8.17.\x*.
\v 7 Naizvozvo vanhu vakauya kuna Mozisi ndokuti\x + Map. 78.34.\x*: Takatadza, nokuti takataura tichipikisa Jehovha nekupikisa imwi\x + 21.5.\x*; nyengeterai kuna Jehovha\x + 1 Zvak. 12.19. 1 Madz. 13.6. Eki. 8.8,28. Mab. 8.24.\x* kuti abvise nyoka kwatiri. Mozisi ndokunyengeterera vanhu\x + 1 Zvak. 12.19. 1 Madz. 13.6. Eki. 8.8,28. Mab. 8.24.\x*.
\v 8 Zvino Jehovha wakati kuna Mozisi: Uzviitire nyoka inopfuta, ugoiisa padanda; zvino zvichaitika kuti umwe neumwe anorumwa paanoitarisa achararama.
\v 9 Zvino Mozisi wakaita nyoka yendarira, ndokuiisa padanda; zvino zvakaitika kuti kana nyoka ikaruma munhu, paanotarisa nyoka yendarira, wakararama\x + 2 Madz. 18.4. Joh. 3.14,15.\x*.
\p
\v 10 Zvino vana vaIsraeri vakabva ndokudzika matende paObhoti\x + 33.43.\x*.
\v 11 Zvino vakabva Obhoti ndokudzika matende paIje-Abharimi murenje rakanangana neMoabhu nechekumabvazuva\x + 33.44.\x*.
\v 12 Vakabvapo vakadzika matende pamupata weZeredhi\x + Det. 2.13.\x*.
\v 13 Vakabvapo vakadzika matende mhiri kweArinoni rwaiva murenje rwuchibuda kumiganhu yeVaAmori; nokuti Arinoni muganhu waMoabhu, pakati paMoabhu neVaAmori\x + 22.36. Vato. 11.18.\x*.
\v 14 Naizvozvo zvinonzi mubhuku reHondo dzaJehovha: Vhahebhi paSufa, nehova dzeArinoni,
\v 15 nemateru ehova dzinosvika kuugaro hweAri, dzinotevedza muganhu waMoabhu\x + 21.28. Det. 2.9,18.29. Isa. 15.1.\x*.
\v 16 Zvino vakabvapo \add vaka\add*enda Bheeri; ndiro tsime Jehovha raakareva kuna Mozisi \add achiti\add*: Unganidza vanhu, zvino ndichavapa mvura\x + Josh. 18.25. Vato. 9.21. 2 Zvak. 20.14.\x*.
\p
\v 17 Ipapo Israeri wakaimba rwiyo urwu: Vhaira, iwe tsime; imwi riimbirei\x + Eki. 15.1.\x*.
\v 18 Machinda akachera tsime iri, makurukota evanhu akarichera, nemupi wemurairo, netsvimbo dzawo\x + Gen. 49.10. Isa. 33.22.\x*. Zvino kubva murenje \add vaka\add*enda Matana;
\v 19 ndokubva Matana kuenda Naharieri; ndokubva Naharieri kuenda Bhamoti;
\v 20 zvino kubva Bhamoti kumupata uri kubani raMoabhu, kunhongonya yePisiga rakatarisa pasi pachiso cherenje\x + 23.28.\x*.
\p
\v 21 Zvino Israeri wakatuma nhume kuna Sihoni mambo weVaAmori achiti\x + Det. 2.26,27. Vato. 11.19.\x*:
\v 22 Rega ndipfuure panyika yako; hatingatsaukiri kuminda kana kuminda yemizambiringa; hatinganwi mvura yetsime; tichafamba nenzira yemambo kusvika tapfuura pamiganhu yako\x + 20.17.\x*.
\v 23 Asi Sihoni haana kutendera Israeri kupfuura nepamiganhu yake; asi Sihoni wakaunganidza vanhu vake vese, ndokubudira kunorwa naIsraeri kurenje\x + Det. 29.7.\x*, zvino wakasvika paJahazi ndokurwa naIsraeri\x + Det. 2.32. Vato. 11.20.\x*.
\v 24 Zvino Israeri wakamurova nekwakapinza kwemunondo ndokuva mwene wenyika yake, kubva paArinoni kusvika paJabhoki kusvika pavana vaAmoni\x + Det. 2.33. Josh. 12.1,2; 24.8. Neh. 9.22. Map. 135.11; 136.19. Amo. 2.9.\x*; nokuti muganhu wevana vaAmoni waiva wakasimba\x + Gen. 32.22.\x*.
\v 25 Zvino Israeri wakatora maguta ose awa; Israeri ndokugara mumaguta ose eVaAmori muHeshibhoni nemumisha yaro yose.
\v 26 Nokuti Heshibhoni raiva guta raSihoni mambo weVaAmori; iye waiva arwa namambo wekutanga waMoabhu, ndokutora nyika yake yose kubva muruoko rwake kusvika paArinoni.
\v 27 Naizvozvo vanoshandisa tsumo vanoti: Uyai muHeshibhoni, guta raSihoni ngarivakwe, risimbiswe\x + Job. 27.1; 29.1. Map. 49.4; 78.2. Isa. 14.4. Mik. 2.4; 23.7.\x*.
\v 28 Nokuti moto wakabuda muHeshibhoni, murazvo paguta raSihoni, wakaparadza Ari weMoabhu, madzishe enzvimbo dzakakwirira dzaArinoni\x + Jer. 48.45,46.\x*.
\v 29 Une nhamo iwe Moabhu\x + Jer. 48.45,46.\x*, maparadzwa, haiwa vanhu veKemoshi\x + Vato. 11.24. 1 Madz. 11.7,33. 2 Madz. 23.13. Jer. 48.7,13.\x*! Wakapa vanakomana kuva vatizi, nevanasikana vake muutapwa, kuna Sihoni mambo weVaAmori.
\v 30 Takavapfura; Heshibhoni rakaparara kusvika kuDhibhoni\x + 32.3,34; 33.45,46. Josh. 13.17. Neh. 11.25? Isa. 15.2. Jer. 48.18,22.\x*; zvino takaaparadza kusvika kuNofa rinosvika kuMedhebha\x + Isa. 15.2.\x*.
\p
\v 31 Israeri ndokugara munyika yeVaAmori.
\v 32 Zvino Mozisi wakatuma kunoshora Jazeri\x + 32.1,3. Josh. 13.25. 2 Zvak. 24.5. Jer. 48.32.\x*; zvino vakatapa misha yaro, ndokudzingira kunze VaAmori vaivapo\x + 21.25.\x*.
\p
\v 33 Zvino vakadzoka ndokukwira nenzira yeBhashani; Ogi mambo weBhashani ndokuvabudira, iye nevanhu vake vese, kuhondo paEdhirei\x + Det. 1.4; 3.1. Josh. 13.12.\x*.
\v 34 Zvino Jehovha wakati kuna Mozisi: Usamutya, nokuti ndamukumikidza muruoko rwako, nevanhu vake vese, nenyika yake\x + Det. 3.2.\x*; zvino uchamuitira sezvawakaitira Sihoni mambo weVaAmori waigara paHeshibhoni\x + 21.24. Det. 29.7. Map. 135.11; 136.20.\x*.
\v 35 Naizvozvo vakamurova nevanakomana vake nevanhu vake vose, kusvika kusina wakapona wakasara kwaari; vakagara nhaka yenyika yake\x + Josh. 10.28.\x*.
